    "description": "地平线科学研究实验室被死寂包围。当你醒来，T12病毒感染导致成百只活死人将你团团包围。<br><br>* 游戏特色 * <br><br>* 完整的战役游戏模式<br>* 支持 2 名玩家的多人合作游戏模式<br>* 8 个挑战——适用于单人或合作游戏的额外游戏模式<br>* 各种枪械和近战武器<br>* 游戏在 3 年来持续不断地免费更新、提供支持和进行改进！<br><br>你需要完成所有实验室关卡并消灭成群的怪物。拥有美国尖端武器，你将选择如何与尸群战斗——无论你决定使用沙鹰还是猎枪！<br><br>为了生存，并拯救世界免受病毒感染，你得用上你的双手和聪明才智：永远不要停止射击，记得随时捡子弹，攀爬水管和梯子，跳上栏杆，抓住绳子，搜索橱柜，把你找到的所有东西都朝僵尸扔过去。<br><br>你可以自由选择武器和战术，向世界证明你的敏捷身手、想象力和无敌枪法。<br><br>不要犹豫，否则你将会被地平线站点的“居民”残酷惩罚。<br><br>游戏特色 :<br><br>●积极运用双手手柄：双手开火，悬挂在绳子上开火，用另一只手给霰弹枪装弹，抓住管道移动，探索难以到达的区域。<br><br>●全套要素：射击、枪、子弹、敌人和鲜血。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/a3172fecf9a46a0dec30ff8552fa989d.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/a3172fecf9a46a0dec30ff8552fa989d.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/a3172fecf9a46a0dec30ff8552fa989d.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 在战斗模式中以单人或与朋友合作进行游戏。与朋友一起游戏更加愉快，更添趣味。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/103d28c5c2ff4fed50ef952ccc323496.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/103d28c5c2ff4fed50ef952ccc323496.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/103d28c5c2ff4fed50ef952ccc323496.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 使用超过 15 种近战武器击溃你的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/bde0e70a80e13fc6c68697279317dafa.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/bde0e70a80e13fc6c68697279317dafa.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/bde0e70a80e13fc6c68697279317dafa.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 你可以选择手动或自动装填弹药。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/ab26e4052f981df92a440a3efb39afd5.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/ab26e4052f981df92a440a3efb39afd5.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/ab26e4052f981df92a440a3efb39afd5.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 升级你的武器，让它们变得与众不同，提升威力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/e326ff222a31804d7905d53fcb1c5f53.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/e326ff222a31804d7905d53fcb1c5f53.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/e326ff222a31804d7905d53fcb1c5f53.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 探索地平线站并寻找隐藏在不同地点的可收集物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/7383f7b2d5e60623426f1aec9d9e925e.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/7383f7b2d5e60623426f1aec9d9e925e.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/7383f7b2d5e60623426f1aec9d9e925e.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● 挑战模式中包含另外 8 种单人或合作游戏模式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/b279017389b0d4bea03b10d267f14325.poster.avif?t=1741967164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/b279017389b0d4bea03b10d267f14325.webm?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829370/extras/b279017389b0d4bea03b10d267f14325.mp4?t=1741967164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
